    "The proposed weight adaption scheme (highlighted in the light orange zone) is designed to trade off the general knowledge of the LLM and the medical expertise of the previous CL model.",
    "The frozen LLM is highlighted in light red, while the conventional teacher and student models are highlighted in light blue.",
    "Ground truth lies in the light green zone.",
